*Put* je veoma dug i težak. (The road is very long and hard.)
Moj put kroz život je bio pun izazova. (My way through life was full of challenges.)
Ona je meni pokazala *put* do odredišta. (She showed me the way to the destination.)
Porodica mi je pomogla da pronađem *put* u životu. (My family helped me to find my way in life.)
Odlučio sam da napravim *put* do njegovog doma. (I decided to make the journey to his home.)
Saznaj koji je *put* najkraći do cilja. (Find out which is the shortest way to the goal.)
On je pronašao *put* da prevaziđe svoje strahove. (He found a way to overcome his fears.)